kipedia.org/wiki/Amanda_Collin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Amanda Collin\">Amanda Collin</a> as Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Arryn\" title=\"Jeyne Arryn\">Jeyne Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Bonnard\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Michelle Bonnard\">Michelle Bonnard</a> as Madam <a href=\"/index.php/Sylvi_(brothel_madam)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sylvi (brothel madam)\">Sylvi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vincent_Regan\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Vincent Regan\">Vincent Regan</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Thorne\" title=\"Rickard Thorne\">Rickard Thorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jordon_Stevens\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Jordon Stevens\">Jordon Stevens</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Elinda_Massey\" title=\"Elinda Massey\">Elinda Massey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maddie_Evans\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maddie Evans\">Maddie Evans</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Dyana\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dyana\">Dyana</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barney_Fishwick\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Barney Fishwick\">Barney Fishwick</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Reyne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Martyn Reyne\">Martyn Reyne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ralph_Davis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ralph Davis\">Ralph Davis</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Leon_Estermont\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Leon Estermont\">Leon Estermont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tok_Stephen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tok Stephen\">Tok Stephen</a> as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Waters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Eddard Waters\">Eddard Waters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Paul_Valentine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paul Valentine\">Paul Valentine</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Germund_Strong\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Germund Strong\">Germund Strong</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Graeme_McKnight\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Graeme McKnight\">Graeme 